Delusional self-belief is a superpower until it's a disasterWhat's the optimal amount of self-deception for a politician? https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/delusional-self-belief-is-a-superpower https://www.ian-leslie.com/p/delusional-self-belief-is-a-superpowerIan Leslie Sat, 02 Mar 2024 09:33:38 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg" width="1160" height="773" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a51693f9-7eba-4304-bf99-fd9bedd84cdf_1160x773.jpeg&