John Burn-Murdoch 已发布了<a href="https://twitter.com/jburnmurdoch/status/1750849189834022932">该文章的调查结果摘要</a>。</p><p>在我们得意忘形之前，让我们记住，这种情况发生在边缘：大多数政治倾向的差异仍然可以在代际之间而不是代际内部找到。<a href="https://twitter.com/jburnmurdoch/status/1750849207567593523">例如</a>，英国的年轻男性在移民问题上可能比年长男性更加自由，这仍然是事实，只是他们在过去几年中并没有变得更加自由，而年轻女性则： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.png" width="1298" height="794" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ddfa658-e7ec-4930-83a6-bfa71f525cbb_1298x794.